creator: Play and be happy
descriptionHtml:
Many packs with many levels there is in this game, packs like halloween 🎃, flags🚩, pirate life🏴‍☠️️ and etc.
New word game with more than 750 levels!
Can you guess which image is answer and Which word parts is answer?
In every level you must guess correct word from 5 word parts and correct image from 5 images, and make a Word Equation!
It is easy but some times can be hard!
Have a good time with solve many puzzles of Word Equations with different subjects!

Many packs with many levels there is in this game, packs like halloween 🎃, flags🚩, pirate life🏴‍☠️️ and etc.
New word game with more than 500 levels!
Can you guess which image is answer and Which word parts is answer?
In every level you must guess correct word from some word parts and correct image from some images, and make a Word Equation!
It is easy but some times can be hard!
Have a good time with solve many puzzles of Word Equations with different subjects!
descriptionShort: 🍹=X+Y , X=DR Y=INK , And many puzzles for solve in this fun word game!
